
FreeRTOS as Xen ARM Guest
-------------------------

This directory, together with the ARM7_CA15_Xen port directory, provides a port
of FreeRTOS for the Cortex A15 ARM processor with support for running as a Xen
guest operating system.

Features provided this port:

 * Generic Interrupt Controller (GIC) setup
 * XenStore configuration and management API
 * Memory page allocator for mapping Xen pages
 * Minimal C library (in platform/minlibc/)
 * Xen console support (output only)
 * Xen inter-domain communication library (platform/libIVC.c)
